						               													<description>A quick shake changes the position of the dice.  Play solo, or take turns to play heat to head with a friend.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Shake &amp;amp; Make is a  pure-luck game that is contained entirely in a single small plastic dome.  Shake the dome and 4 dice fall into slots to display 4 random numbers.  A rulebook (attached to the bottom of the dome) summarized different patterns, mostly following Yahtzee/Poker pattern rankings.  Play solo for the best combination or competitively by comparing to see who rolled the best pattern.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Take turns to see who can get the best score - Highest total, 1 pair, 2 pair, straight, 3-of-a-kind, 4-of-a-kind...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Do you have the luck to shake and make the best roll?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
